#!/usr/bin/env bash

cat <<'EOF'
GNU Automake — generates portable Makefile.in files for use with autoconf.

This plugin lists versions from https://github.com/autotools-mirror/automake
and builds them from the official GNU release tarballs (ftp.gnu.org), which
ship a pre-generated ./configure.

Build requirements: autoconf, perl, make. If you manage autoconf with asdf,
install and activate it before building automake.
EOF
